  "style": "",
  "texts": [
    "After creating a manual dataset of about 3,000 emails in each category from both work and personal accounts, a few entries from already existing datasets were added to expand the diversity.",
    "After merging the newly collected emails with existing datasets, we conducted an emotionmotivation labeling phase using multiple LLMs.",
    "Each model was benchmarked on its ability to detect emotional cues and attacker motivations, allowing us to compare accuracy, consistency, and agreement with human annotations.",
    "Once the most reliable model was identified, it was used to label the full dataset.",
    "To validate the quality of this labeling, a subset of 100 emails was manually reviewed by two experts-a psychology specialist and a cyber-awareness analystto ensure alignment between LLM-derived and human-interpreted emotional signals."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}